```

## Reconciliation

When the WS gateway emits an assistant frame carrying `conversation_id`, the existing observer machinery already keys by conv. Add an OTID-keyed lookup so the user-side echo (if/when Letta returns a server-stored `user_message` matching the OTID) replaces the optimistic one cleanly.

